INSERT INTO `wp_options` VALUES("2111", "options-framework-theme", "a:12:{s:4:\"logo\";s:78:\"http://empyrealsolutions.azurewebsites.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/logo.png\";s:10:\"copyrights\";s:35:\"Copyright - Empyreal Solutions 2015\";s:7:\"welcome\";s:479:\"<h3>Welcome To Empyreal Solutions</h3>\r\n<p>We are a boutique Cloud &amp; Managed Services provider based in South Australia that focuses on working with clients with a high degree of personalised service through our advisory and business consulting services. We specialise in private, hybrid and public cloud solutions from design, through to deployment and ongoing managed support.\r\n</p> <p> Trust us to transform your ICT into a modernised platform that will help your business\";s:8:\"about_us\";s:415:\"<h4>About Us</h4>\r\n<p>Empyreal Solutions was born in 2013 to meet local market demand in Cloud and Managed Services for clients across the K-12 and SMB verticals who were unhappy with a generic approach to service from their incumbent ICT partner. Our focus is to ensure your investment in ICT is realised to its full potential, with peace of mind knowing that it is reliable, secure and performing at its best.</p>\";s:5:\"cloud\";s:549:\"<h4>Cloud Technologies</h4>\r\n<p>We specialise in the design, delivery and support of Microsoft Cloud technologies such as Office 365 and Azure. Whether you have an existing investment in on premise technology or are looking at moving to the cloud for a new venture, Empyreal Solutions can work with you to ensure the best possible outcome for your business. We offer month by month subscription based services for your users to realise the benefits of Office 365 or a complete managed \"Office in the Cloud\" solution, hosted with Microsoft Azure.</p>\";s:10:\"it_managed\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"latest_technologies\";s:1:\"5\";s:13:\"service_title\";s:12:\"Our Services\";s:17:\"testimonial_title\";s:19:\"Client Testimonials\";s:8:\"facebook\";s:9:\"#Facebook\";s:7:\"twitter\";s:8:\"#